’Ů@2b5f6206ffbb0e00ad353fccf1114f66dcdc9b5e19c40facee56d020943570afÚYTitle: title: term size
Path: Examples
Content:
Return the columns (width) and rows (height) of the terminal.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> term size


```
Return the columns (width) of the terminal.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> (term size).columns


```
Return the rows (height) of the terminal.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> (term size).rows


```
